Sangfor Technologies, a manufacturer of network equipments including WAN optimization, Next-Generation Firewall, and SSL VPN, sells its products mainly to midsize enterprises.
Established in 2000, Sangfor Technologies has around 28,000 clients and 2,300 employees worldwide (2015). Sangfor has 55 branches, including Overseas branches in the US, UK, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia, Singapore and Hong Kong.
